snippet.textDisplay:
Stupid Question Incoming:
At 16:43, Linus shows how fast they were downloading off of a number of launchers. How is it that he is able to achieve such high installation speeds? I currently have 100 mbps Download speed and mine barely gets above 14 mbps on Steam and Battlenet when downloading a game or update. I am going through a Powerline Adapter but I still get 100+ mbps down when i check my speed on Ookley Speedtest. These are also going onto an SSD so there is no bottleneck there. I was always told that the launchers purposely bottleneck download speeds to help server stability. I am just wondering if there is a way to increase my download speeds without having to get Gigabit connection.
